  "original_title": "Waiting for resignation serves no purpose; elect new Prez through Parliament: JVP",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Waiting for resignation serves no purpose; elect new Prez through Parliament: JVP",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Claiming that it was absurd waiting anymore for the President\u2019s resignation, as he had fled the country disregarding his responsibility, the Janatha Vimukthi Peramuna said today Parliament had a right to elect a new President as per the Constitution.",
        "JVP MP Vijitha Herath told a news conference that if the President had not officially tendered his resignation, it could be presumed as vacating the post.",
        "He said there was a similar incident where Tunisian President Ben Ali fled the country without announcing his\u00a0 offical resignation.",
        "MP Herath said in terms with the provisions of the Article 38(2) of the Constitution, the Speaker and the Chief Justice can take a decision to elect a new President thorugh Parlaiment.",
        "He said both the President and the Prime Minister should step down to stabilise and bring back the country to normalcy. (Ajith Siriwardana)"
      ],
